# Input
```html
<!-- should generate diagnostics -->
<!doctype html>
<html>
<head>
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="./styles.css">
</head>
<body>
	<!-- ghost is not in styles.css -->
	<div class="ghost">Not defined anywhere</div>
	<!-- card is defined, so only ghost is flagged -->
	<div class="card">Valid class</div>
</body>
</html>

```

